# 调度与相机规范

## CameraController 接口
```typescript
interface CameraController {
  readonly type: '2d' | '25d' | '3d';
  readonly state: CameraState;      // 来自 L0/types
  readonly isAnimating: boolean;
  readonly inertiaEnabled: boolean;
  readonly constraints: CameraConstraints;

  setCenter(center: [number, number]): void;
  setZoom(zoom: number): void;
  setBearing(bearing: number): void;   // 弧度，禁止用 heading
  setPitch(pitch: number): void;       // 弧度
  jumpTo(options: { center?; zoom?; bearing?; pitch? }): void;
  flyTo(options: { center?; zoom?; bearing?; pitch?; altitude?; duration?; easing? }): CameraAnimation;
  easeTo(options: { center?; zoom?; bearing?; pitch?; duration? }): CameraAnimation;
  stop(): void;
  setConstraints(c: Partial<CameraConstraints>): void;
  setInertiaEnabled(enabled: boolean): void;

  update(deltaTime: number, viewport: Viewport): CameraState;
  handlePanStart(screenX: number, screenY: number): void;
  handlePanMove(screenX: number, screenY: number): void;
  handlePanEnd(): void;
  handleZoom(delta: number, screenX: number, screenY: number): void;
  handleRotate(bearingDelta: number, pitchDelta: number): void;

  onMoveStart(cb: () => void): () => void;
  onMove(cb: (state: CameraState) => void): () => void;
  onMoveEnd(cb: () => void): () => void;
  destroy(): void;
}

interface CameraConstraints {
  minZoom: number; maxZoom: number;
  minPitch: number; maxPitch: number;
  maxBounds?: BBox2D;
}
```

## Camera2D
- 正交投影 `mat4.ortho()`
- bearing=0 pitch=0（固定）
- 惯性：速度采样最近 5 帧 + 指数衰减
- flyTo：Bezier 曲线在 zoom/center 空间插值

## Camera25D
- 透视 `mat4.perspectiveReversedZ()`
- bearing/pitch 可变，maxPitch 约束
- 惯性：pan+rotate+pitch 独立衰减
- 高 pitch 自动调整 far plane

## Camera3D
- ECEF 坐标系，`perspectiveReversedZInfinite()`
- 四元数旋转（heading/pitch/roll → bearing/pitch/roll）
- **地形碰撞**：异步查询 DEM 高度 + 平滑约束
- 惯性：四元数 slerp 衰减
- flyTo：Great Circle Arc + 高度抛物线
- 额外方法：`setPosition(lon,lat,alt)` / `lookAt()` / `queryTerrainHeight()` / `setTerrainCollisionEnabled()`

## ViewMorph
- `morphTo(targetMode, fromCamera, toCamera, options)` → ViewMorphAnimation
- 2D→25D：线性插值 pitch + ortho→perspective 渐变
- 2D→3D：两阶段（pitch 升起 → 墨卡托→ECEF 顶点变形 + 投影混合）
- 过渡期：两个相机同时计算，RenderGraph 使用混合矩阵

## TileScheduler
```typescript
interface TileScheduler {
  update(camera: CameraState, viewport: Viewport): TileScheduleResult;
  registerSource(sourceId: string, options: TileSourceOptions): void;
  unregisterSource(sourceId: string): void;
  getVisibleTiles(sourceId: string): TileCoord[];
  onTileLoaded(sourceId: string, coord: TileCoord, data: any): void;
  onTileError(sourceId: string, coord: TileCoord, error: Error): void;
  reloadAll(): void;
  clearCache(sourceId?: string): void;
}
interface TileScheduleResult {
  toLoad: TilePriority[];      // 按优先级排序
  toUnload: TileCoord[];
  visible: TileCoord[];
  placeholder: Map<string, TileCoord>;  // 缺失瓦片替代
}
```
- SSE（Screen Space Error）驱动 LOD
- 高 pitch 远处降低优先级
- Placeholder：父瓦片替代未加载的子瓦片

## FrameScheduler
- 四阶段：UPDATE → RENDER → POST_FRAME → IDLE
- `hasBudget()` 检查帧预算
- Page Visibility 自动降频
- `requestRenderMode` 仅变化时渲染
